	<h2>What is {$domain.pagetitle}?</h2>
	<p>{$domain.pagetitle} is a free online golf tracking service which can help you improve your game. By recording and entering your round scorecards {$domain.pagetitle} can help you visualise your game and show you where it needs improvement and help.<br /><br />{$domain.pagetitle} has a club directory which contains all of the clubs within the UK and Ireland. We're adding more clubs from Europe very soon (France, Spain and Portugal to start with).<br /><br />{$domain.pagetitle} also has an online shop with over 2000 products available. All at great prices.</p>
	<a name="two"></a>
	<h2>Do I have to pay to use {$domain.pagetitle}?</h2>
	<p>No! All of {$domain.pagetitle}'s game tracking and analysis is 100% free to use. Forever.</p>
	<a name="three"></a>
	<h2>How can {$domain.pagetitle} improve my game?</h2>
	<p>{$domain.pagetitle} let's you see your game like never before! This makes it easy to pick up where shots could be saved with extra practice on the driving range or putting green. Once you've added some scorecards to the system, visit the tracking centre and start seeing how your game shapes up.<br /><br />By adding extra stats such as FIR, GIR and number of putts taken per hole, you'll get a much better experience and more useful, game improving stats!</p>
	<a name="four"></a>
	<h2>Why do I need to sign-up to use {$domain.pagetitle}?</h2>
	<p>In order to store and analyse your round data on {$domain.pagetitle}, we need to associate your data with you via an account. Once your account is created you can then log-in and view your data.</p>
	<a name="five"></a>
	<h2>I'd like to buy from the shop. Is {$domain.pagetitle} secure?</h2>
	<p>Yes. {$domain.pagetitle} uses an industry standard SSL certificate, which means all sensitive data transmitted from our site to the bank is encrypted.</p>

